<plot>Inside an old fashion toy store, a beautiful princess doll is labeled 'broken' and repeatedly thrown into a rejects box by a succession of unforgiving children. Set in the belief that only a toy of comparable eminence can save her from this fate, the princess waits within the darkness for her prince charming to come. When her hero arrives in the form of a fellow reject, who less than fulfills her expectations, the princess is faced with a reality she does not want to accept.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?429001</url></doc>
